dnl @synopsis AC_CXX_COMPLEX_MATH_IN_NAMESPACE_STD
dnl
dnl If the C math functions are in the cmath header file and std:: namespace,
dnl define HAVE_MATH_FN_IN_NAMESPACE_STD.
dnl
